test_unit_budget_search
  record_type "meta_test"
  suite "budget_search"
  test_file "tests/unit/budget_search.rs"
  pins "The fixture reachability problem is solved under a sufficient budget, stays unknown with search: evidence under budget 0, is deterministic across runs and instances, respects the allowed operator set, is recognised across en/ru/hi/zh, proposes a gated (never promotable) skill on success, and stays inert for ordinary calculations."
